{"lang": "en_US", "eventid": "main_16", "eventName": "Abnormal Spectrum", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "EG-8", "avgTag": "Interlude", "storyName": "Events of the Past", "storyInfo": "A sunken city resurfaces. An abandoned mining lamp is relit. Anything can happen in times like these.\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g5_deepmine", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Th-The guns have stopped.", "name": "Timid Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "C-Can we go now? Not upwards, but down, before the bombs reach us—", "name": "Timid Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,-50", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Get up, Yuri, and the rest of you. We need to find Rankin and the place he was talking about.", "name": "Worried Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "You know the bravest ones of us have all left with Rankin, to take the outpost.", "name": "Worried Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "The bombing's stopped, and we don't know what's going on up there. The only way to find them is up.", "name": "Worried Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Either we save them, or, as Rankin said, remember them. Crawl, pull yourselves on with your pickaxes, if you can't walk.", "name": "Worried Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "But Rankin gave us his mining lamp—", "name": "Timid Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Do you remember what he said?", "name": "Worried Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "He... he didn't say anything...", "name": "Timid Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "That's right. He didn't say anything. This is no different from the supplies that they left behind.", "name": "Worried Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Or we can choose to leave it here... as a reminder.", "name": "Worried Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Yes, reminder. Leave the lamp in the mining cart, the one that we pushed all the way here.", "name": "Worried Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "If anyone ever comes through...", "name": "Worried Miner"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "I remember that you can write, Yuri.", "name": "Worried Miner"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_papertear", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "We've got some blank pages at the back of the logbook. We might as well not waste it.", "name": "Worried Miner"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Come here. I'll tell you what to write.", "name": "Worried Miner"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "If anyone comes, at least they'll know what happened here.", "name": "Worried Miner"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_iceforest_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>A mine, Northern Tundra, Ursus</><p=2>Winter, 1101</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_both", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_094", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Sir, where... where are we going?", "name": "Sick Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_094"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "I don't think the factory's this way—", "name": "Sick Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_094"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_082"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Shut up and keep walking.", "name": "Soldier"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_082"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "I said walk!", "name": "Soldier"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_082"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "(Whisper) The mines have stopped again.", "name": "Skeptical Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "(Whisper) So, nothing for the processing plants to work with.", "name": "Skeptical Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "(Whisper) Where would they take us, if they don't need hands upstairs?", "name": "Skeptical Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "They dragged even the sickest ones out of their beds. Half the mine is here...", "name": "Fearful Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "I don't want to keep walking. I don't want to die!", "name": "Fearful Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "(Whisper) Shh!", "name": "Skeptical Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "Army Officer"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Go through the forest, to the lake. That's where you'll meet your end.", "name": "Army Officer"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Don't even think...", "name": "Army Officer"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "About running away.", "name": "Army Officer"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Heavy military boots step on the snowy forest floor, moving forward, urging forward."}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "The miners are being escorted by far more than just a few men."}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snow_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Here. Stop.", "name": "Army Officer"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Let's begin.", "name": "Army Officer"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_082"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Everyone, on the ice.", "name": "Soldier"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_082"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "No, sir, please—", "name": "Fearful Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 1.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_broadswordblood", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-50", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "The saber cuts her throat, spilling hot blood on the soldier's armor."}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "For the glory of Ursus.", "name": "Army Officer"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_094"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "<i>Bozhe moy</i>...", "name": "Sick Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_094"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Proceed.", "name": "Army Officer"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_082"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "N-Next! Fill the gap! Hurry!", "name": "Soldier"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_082"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_surfacefrozen", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "sur"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "sur", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Why do we have to be treated like this?", "name": "Skeptical Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_082"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Shut up, you <i>uyobok</i>—", "name": "Soldier"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_082"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Were the Tsar's promises all a lie? Are our lives worth less than that of a burdenbeast?", "name": "Skeptical Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Tell me—", "name": "Skeptical Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "Army Officer"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "As the soldier is about to raise his hand again, the rumbling of the ground becomes perceptible."}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "It starts with a tiny crack, from the surface, from deep below, before snowballing quickly."}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_erthshkng", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "e"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 4.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 90.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "e", "fadetime": 6.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_surfacefrozen", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "The ground trembles, and the center of the lake collapses. The result of geological changes accumulated over time swallows the Infected on the ice, and their would-be executioners."}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Run!", "name": "Skeptical Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "The miner shakes off the stunned soldier and runs in the direction they came from."}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Catastrophe...", "name": "Terrified Miner"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "It's a Catastrophe!!!", "name": "Terrified Miner"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_thunders_amb", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_erthshkng", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "e"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 4.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 90.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "e", "fadetime": 6.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spirlstrsndlss", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rockfall", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Soldier, miner. Killer, victim. The vast Lake Angara accepts all and delivers all."}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Beneath the ice, an ancient nomadic city rises as the terrain changes, emerging through the sheet into the light of day."}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "The old-style buildings and the writhing faces of the dead look the same as they did when the city sank."}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g10_tent_inside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>Reconstruction District, Far North, Ursus</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_only_heavy", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "'Northern Tundra'... 'Catastrophe'... 'Lake'...", "name": "Diligent Miner"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "All those words crammed into this tiny space, and I only recognize three.", "name": "Diligent Miner"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "You'll learn them in time.", "name": "Young Craftsman"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "The lessons here are too basic for me. I'm planning to take over the work at the mines, which has been left untended for a while, and maybe learn a craft other than shoe repair.", "name": "Young Craftsman"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Once the curfew is lifted, I want to go to Deity Grypherburg.", "name": "Young Craftsman"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "I don't want to go to Grypherburg. I just want to learn to read. Three words a day makes twenty-one a week. In one month...", "name": "Diligent Miner"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_highheelfts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_415_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "I'm glad to see your eagerness.", "name": "Koshelna"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Do you need help?", "name": "Koshelna"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "These words still confuse me, <i>gospozha</i>.", "name": "Diligent Miner"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_415_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "You're talking about these 'nouns', right? That's the lesson for this week—we're learning about nouns.", "name": "Koshelna"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Nouns, yes! Nouns. I think I'm starting to be able to tell them apart, but I can't quite get their meanings.", "name": "Diligent Miner"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "What's this... uh... 'Shimok'?", "name": "Diligent Miner"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_415_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Ah...", "name": "Koshelna"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "It's 'Simonch'. It's a name, like the name 'Angara', the lake, or your name, 'Vova'.", "name": "Koshelna"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "It's the name of a nomadic city.", "name": "Koshelna"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g5_deepmine", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_energywell", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "en"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.8, "channel": "en", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "The youth bids his classmate farewell and goes into the mines, ready to get to work."}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Mine tunnels left untended gradually wear down and eventually collapse. He will not allow it to happen, as long as he is still here."}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "The young man raises his mining lamp and begins his rounds, examining all the rail, until he finds a mining cart at one of the forks that does not belong to this place."}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "This is...", "name": "Young Craftsman"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "A mining lamp?", "name": "Young Craftsman"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "And a letter—", "name": "Young Craftsman"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "Young Craftsman"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "This was once the place of a struggle?", "name": "Young Craftsman"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Damn it. The people who proposed connecting the mining districts were here! They wanted to occupy that garrisoned outpost!", "name": "Young Craftsman"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "I knew the story was true...", "name": "Young Craftsman"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "en", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "66_i20", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.05, "yScaleFrom": 1.05, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cndlbrn", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_churchfire", "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Phew...", "name": "Young Craftsman"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Whoever's lamp this was, it's in good condition. Maybe a little dusty, but it still works...", "name": "Young Craftsman"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Maybe I should take it to Grypherburg—", "name": "Young Craftsman"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "And show everyone...", "name": "Young Craftsman"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "This lamp without a name, and those people without names.", "name": "Young Craftsman"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "en", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}